Here are a ton of those pieces all combined into one video. If you’re in the market for a Tesla Model 3, you’ll need to go through a number of considerations in choosing to purchase, tips when purchasing your Tesla Model 3, Accessories that you need for your Tesla Model 3, and last, I’m providing a handful of fun pieces that I didn’t expect! 

I hope you find this helpful and if so, please help me out with a like and subscribing!
